{
  "info": {
    "name": "rfq_chatbot_ms - Phase 6 Demo Beats v1",
    "_postman_id": "rfq-chatbot-phase6-demo-v1",
    "description": "Step 13 Postman demo beats for Phase 6.\n\nScope:\n- Fourteen scripted beats matching Pack K.2.\n- Uses local stack endpoints.\n- Follows the Phase 5 collection structure (folder per scenario, setup request, turn request(s), assertions).\n\nRun order:\n1) 0 - Bootstrap\n2) 1..12 - Phase 6 scenario beats\n3) 13 - Phase 5 regression reference beat\n4) 14 - Mode B general knowledge beat\n\nManual notes:\n- Scenario 7 may require temporarily stopping rfq_manager_ms to force retrieval failure.\n- Scenario 12 requires checking service logs for phase6.grounding_gap_absence_injected=true and phase6.output_guardrail_result=pass while HTTP response remains 200.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('run_suffix')) {",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('run_suffix', String(Date.now()));",
          "}",
          "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('marker_text')) {",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('marker_text', 'Confidence: pattern-based (validated against 1 sample)');",
          "}",
          "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('user_prefix')) {",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('user_prefix', 'phase6-demo');",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
